# Diagrams

PlantUML sources + rendered SVGs for the <project> architecture. Each `.puml` has a sibling `.svg` checked in so the diagrams render directly in GitHub / VS Code / Foxglove without re-running PlantUML.

## Files

One diagram per file, each renders independently:

| Diagram | Source | Rendered |
|---|---|---|
| Node map (layer geography) | [`node-map.puml`](node-map.puml) | [`node-map.svg`](node-map.svg) |
| Data-flow overview (read first) | [`data-flow-overview.puml`](data-flow-overview.puml) | [`data-flow-overview.svg`](data-flow-overview.svg) |
| Sensing chain | [`data-flow-sensing.puml`](data-flow-sensing.puml) | [`data-flow-sensing.svg`](data-flow-sensing.svg) |
| Control chain | [`data-flow-control.puml`](data-flow-control.puml) | [`data-flow-control.svg`](data-flow-control.svg) |
| Safety chain | [`data-flow-safety.puml`](data-flow-safety.puml) | [`data-flow-safety.svg`](data-flow-safety.svg) |
| Operator + persistence | [`data-flow-operator.puml`](data-flow-operator.puml) | [`data-flow-operator.svg`](data-flow-operator.svg) |
| TF tree | [`data-flow-tf.puml`](data-flow-tf.puml) | [`data-flow-tf.svg`](data-flow-tf.svg) |

